text:
“ The thing about my brother, he wasn't afraid to be his own man. — Prince Liam about his brother [src] ”

Prince Robert Henstridge was the 23-year-old Prince of England, and the future king after his father. Robert was the firstborn son of Simon Henstridge and Helena Henstridge and was also the half-older brother of Liam Henstridge and Eleanor Henstridge.
